token_lists.title: ＴＯＰＯＳ ＳＥＲＩＥＳ
token_lists.description:
TOPOS SERIES departs from high resolution satellite images of the Amazon forest. Through the use of a high contrast image treatment, I abstracted the forest - which became all black - and emphasized the human interventions on it. This series proposes a reflection on the future of the greatest forest of our planet, in a time when its destruction is at its highest rate.

I minted this series for the #BNW22 event in Versum.

token_lists.title: Fragments of Reality
token_lists.description:
Fragments of Reality is a project born in collaboration between Simone Pompei and Salvatore Caruso. It is a transversal experiment between generative art and photography.

Reality is perceived through fragments of images and memories. Sometimes they overlap and intertwine forming new thoughts or images.

Generative art by Simone Pompei
Photography by Salvatore Caruso
